cu.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid_verbosity' will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an unknown enum 'invalid_verbosity' will cause configuration validation failure and prevent proper initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid_verbosity'，會導致配置驗證失敗，並阻止正確的初始化。
